{"tid":761171,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得kris lau有妄想症","createTime":"2018-07-30T07:16:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T07:20:25.000Z","uid":84006,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e394072a2f1ac9e014746d6c39ad08109d1df10b","tid":761171,"uid":84006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:16:28.000Z","msg":"我有個fd d症狀同佢一模一樣 最後入左青山<br />\n<br />\n以為自己好撚勁 有啲乜野過人之處<br />\n認為所有批評佢既人都係妒忌佢/害佢<br />\n所以聽到有人批評 會選擇無視/迴避<br />\n當比人迫到佢無得迴避嗰陣<br />\n就會瘋狂洗版 洗到自己覺得舒服<br />\n<br />\n以前我都試過同我個fd講道理<br />\n但係我個fd做既野同佢完全一樣<br />\n然後我先醒覺<br />\n精神病人係有d生理缺陷<br />\n所以點罵佢點講道理都係無用<br />\n佢地都唔會明白/唔會聽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且妄想症其中一個最麻煩既地方 就係患者智力無障礙 唔會覺得自己有病/有問題 只會覺得係其他人有問題/害佢<br />\n不過妄想症只要唔係太嚴重都可以好似個正常人咁生活<br />\n所以唔好上咁多連登啦kris 一陣受得太大刺激入埋青山就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e106d58c108f61ac2db0d78c903677e1e67f2027","tid":761171,"uid":189724,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:17:09.000Z","msg":"邊個係kris lau?"},{"pid":"d4ce419435576aacacfd5c2a8f7732d6e8c2e347","tid":761171,"uid":151969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:35:55.000Z","msg":"邊位"},{"pid":"7d2ae40dcd332e89335622b2fa7eee8d033ca733","tid":761171,"uid":135645,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:16:38.000Z","msg":"Who"},{"pid":"61b388bfa73dbb671872ef2bfc5429be8f26ab08","tid":761171,"uid":188201,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"quote":{"pid":"e394072a2f1ac9e014746d6c39ad08109d1df10b","tid":761171,"uid":84006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:16:28.000Z","msg":"我有個fd d症狀同佢一模一樣 最後入左青山<br />\n<br />\n以為自己好撚勁 有啲乜野過人之處<br />\n認為所有批評佢既人都係妒忌佢/害佢<br />\n所以聽到有人批評 會選擇無視/迴避<br />\n當比人迫到佢無得迴避嗰陣<br />\n就會瘋狂洗版 洗到自己覺得舒服<br />\n<br />\n以前我都試過同我個fd講道理<br />\n但係我個fd做既野同佢完全一樣<br />\n然後我先醒覺<br />\n精神病人係有d生理缺陷<br />\n所以點罵佢點講道理都係無用<br />\n佢地都唔會明白/唔會聽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且妄想症其中一個最麻煩既地方 就係患者智力無障礙 唔會覺得自己有病/有問題 只會覺得係其他人有問題/害佢<br />\n不過妄想症只要唔係太嚴重都可以好似個正常人咁生活<br />\n所以唔好上咁多連登啦kris 一陣受得太大刺激入埋青山就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:06:37.000Z","msg":"其實有神技跟住唔使改卷係妄想症嘅一種？<br />\nBilly ng 上東網<br />\nBilly ng mock exam 係信心嘅保證<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/17/184438_1a712181a0e2ba7ccc17e63a09b498cf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F184438_1a712181a0e2ba7ccc17e63a09b498cf.png&h=b2f2ecf2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/17/184440_164510c8a6e876cef5eb67d84a2ac6e4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F184440_164510c8a6e876cef5eb67d84a2ac6e4.png&h=bb39236b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/17/184441_b8883a0859f7f34265be1dc5887ef457.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F184441_b8883a0859f7f34265be1dc5887ef457.png&h=9511eb54&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/17/184444_926bba67724ef3fb411986a6dd7578b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F184444_926bba67724ef3fb411986a6dd7578b6.png&h=d3ec0eba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"198622cbf780cd4c11e16a1ed41a1d027c488d10","tid":761171,"uid":177094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:25:17.000Z","msg":"笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04589d4060dd99f6fc2c1498d6cae1b1b5ec8a1","tid":761171,"uid":188396,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"61b388bfa73dbb671872ef2bfc54